            . I am a constable. I went to Mr. Drew's about ten o'clock on this night. I did not see the prisoner there, but while I was there, I heard a cry of Stop thief! outside.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. On Saturday evening I was at Drew's.</p>
